OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,FA father whose pregnant partner
OL,7,Fshouted at him to "grow up" as he
OL,8,Ftried to set fire to a hotel housing
OL,9,Fasylum seekers during rioting in
OL,10,FRotherham has been jailed.
OL,12,FMason Lowe, of Lowfield Road, Bolton-
OL,13,Fupon-Dearne in South Yorkshire, was
OL,14,Fpart of a mob who attacked the Holiday
OL,15,FInn Express in Manvers on 4 August
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,18,FStaff were forced to barricade
OL,19,Fthemselves inside as the violence
OL,20,Fescalated.
