OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,FA flaming wheelie bin was pushed up
OL,7,Fagainst a hotel fire door, effectively
OL,8,Ftrapping those inside.
OL,10,FPluming engineer Lowe, 28, propped a
OL,11,Fpiece of plywood across the fire door,
OL,12,Fmeaning a police officer inside was
OL,13,Funable to direct a fire extinguisher
OL,14,Fonto the bin, Sheffield Crown Court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FMasked and draped with a flag of St
OL,18,FGeorge, he goaded police and pushed
OL,19,Fout at an officer.
