OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,FHe also attacked police who were
OL,7,Ftrying to protect the 200 terrified
OL,8,Fresidents.
OL,10,FThe court heard Lowe's heavily
OL,11,Fpregnant partner shouted at him: "Grow
OL,12,Fup or do not f***ing come home."
OL,14,FLowe was jailed for seven years and
OL,15,Fsix months after he admitted arson
OL,16,Fwith intent to endanger life and
OL,17,Fviolent disorder.
OL,19,FTrainee barber Morgan Heeley, a father-
OL,20,Fof-two, was also sentenced for his
OL,21,Frole in the riot.
