OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,FHeeley, of Margaret Road, Darfield in
OL,7,FBarnsley, was seen placing a lit item
OL,8,Finside the wheelie bin.
OL,10,FHe shoved over a female officer,
OL,11,Fsmashed a large hotel window, which
OL,12,Fraised a cheer from the crowd, and
OL,13,Ftried to set fire to hotel curtains.
OL,15,FHeeley, 26, also opened a door on a
OL,16,Fpolice riot van, threw missiles at
OL,17,Fofficers and used a fire extinguisher
OL,18,Fon police.
