OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to eight years after
OL,7,Fpleading guilty to the same charges.
OL,8,FThe judge, Jeremy Richardson KC,
OL,9,Fextended both their licence periods by
OL,10,Fthree years.
OL,12,FHe told the pair: "The disorder was
OL,13,Fracist and extremely frightening for
OL,14,Fanyone who was there.
OL,16,F"Even though both of you deny this, I
OL,17,Fam also sure you had a racist mindset
OL,18,Fat the time.
