OL,3,CJail for rioter told 'grow up or don't
OL,4,Ccome home' by pregnant partner
OL,6,F"What took place in Rotherham that day
OL,7,Fhad nothing whatever to do with
OL,8,Flegitimate political protest, it was a
OL,9,Fdesire to perpetrate racist mob rule
OL,10,Fand to commit very serious criminal
OL,11,Foffences in the process.
OL,13,F"You were both in the thick of it and
OL,14,Feach played a prominent role. You are
OL,15,Fboth unquestionably dangerous
OL,16,Foffenders.
OL,18,F"It is to be hoped the racist
OL,19,Fmalignancy within you both can be
OL,20,Feradicated whilst in custody."
